728188f-a.title: Queens: Welling Court - 30th Avenue
728188f-a.text:
(1) 29 Welling Court (old number), west of 30th Ave. (right not shown.) The white house was about a century old when Roe H. Smith purchased it. One Allen was the owner in 1934. Roe H. Smith  occupied it in 1840.
